              <p class="mlp-welcome-sub">Your personal code workspace — create, manage &amp; share HTML, CSS and JS projects. Everything is saved right in your browser.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mlp-welcome-steps">
            <div class="mlp-welcome-step">
              <span class="mlp-welcome-step-num">1</span>
