                <span>Click <em>New Project</em> to give it a name and description.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mlp-welcome-step">
              <span class="mlp-welcome-step-num">2</span>
              <div class="mlp-welcome-step-body">
                <strong>Write your code</strong>
                <span>Use the built-in editor with HTML, CSS &amp; JS tabs and a live preview.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mlp-welcome-step">
              <span class="mlp-welcome-step-num">3</span>
              <div class="mlp-welcome-step-body">
                <strong>Share it</strong>
                <span>Publish your project and get a shareable link to show it off.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button id="mlp-welcome-create-btn" class="mlp-welcome-cta" type="button">
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
