              <p class="mlp-partner-desc">This is a Discord community dedicated to helping YOU learn how to code, from home, for free. Whether you're a beginner or a full time developer, or if you've never touched a piece of code, there is a place for you in our community. Join Today! https://discord.gg/94Gn5YKpuj</p>
